lead_paragraph: Just the prospect of Lionel Messi's return gave Argentina so much confidence that one player openly said it would intimidate the Brazilians ahead of their South American World Cup qualifying match.

headline.print_headline: Brazil's Neymar Takes Honors, Messi Returns for Argentina
